h zeitgenössischen Notizen niedergeschrieben, werden hier erstmals vollständig veröffentlicht.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a FA license: uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/free-access-policy uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh1 aKotze, Hildegard von, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History <1990z9783110635829oZDB-23-GHI40uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/9783486703528zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486703528zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486703528/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GHIb1990  aZDB-23-GOA